summary: PostgreSQL conformance tests
description: |
    Runs the 31-test conformance suite and 6 migration tests against
    PostgreSQL. DynamoDB conformance runs in GitHub Actions CI. SQLite
    and inmem conformance run as part of unit tests.
test: bash tests/conformance/run.sh
duration: 10m
require:
    - golang
    - docker
    - docker-compose
    - curl
framework: shell
